1.0.name: wordpress/thoof-submit-and-rank
1.0.description: Allows easy submission of your posts to Thoof and will display the ThoofRank of your post once submitted. If there is already a ThoofRank button on an article, the plugin will not display another one.Email support@thoof.com if you have any problems.
